<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǒu yī tiáo jiāng hé 迦南1359</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu yī tiáo jiāng hé zhèng cóng zhè lǐ liú guò yào liú biàn měi yī gè jiǎo luò
 jiù shì shèng líng de jiāng hé yǒng bù zhǐ xī de jiāng hé zhèng jiāo guàn gāo mǒ nǐ hé wǒ
 wū yún dōu xiāo sàn zhòng dān dōu tuō luò zàn měi zhǔ cì xià bǎo zuò
 wǒ men jìng bài yé sū wǒ men kǒu chàng xīn hé chàng bù wán gǎn ēn de gē
 yǒu yī tiáo jiāng hé zhèng cóng zhè lǐ liú guò liǎng àn huā xiāng guǒ zi duō
 yǒu yī tiáo jiāng hé zhèng cóng zhè lǐ liú guò shān pō shàng niú yáng duō
 shān pō shàng niú yáng duō</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1359</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>